 2​​023 年在马德里 Primavera Sound 演出。图片来源：Mariano Regidor/Redferns" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Christine-and-the-Queens-performs-at-Primavera-Sound-Madrid-in-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据歌手医生的建议， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christine-and-the-queens" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Christine and the Queens</a>取消了 2023 年所有剩余的巡演日期。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/christine-and-the-queens-live-in-paris-review-redcar-cirque-dhiver-3346899" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>克里斯汀和皇后们住在巴黎：进入雷德卡世界的超现实奇幻之旅</strong></a></li></ul><p>今天（10 月 16 日）早些时候，克里斯汀和皇后乐队的官方 Instagram 账户传出了取消的消息。帖子中写道：“Red（又名克里斯汀和皇后乐队）今天生病了，根据医生的建议，被迫做出艰难的决定，取消 2023 年所有剩余的巡演日期。”目前尚不清楚是什么疾病导致取消。</p><p>克里斯汀和皇后乐队原定今天在蒙特利尔演出，这是更广泛的北美巡演的一部分，该巡演将持续到 10 月 26 日，届时他将出现在芝加哥的维克剧院。此后，克里斯汀和皇后乐队计划在欧洲各地进行一系列演出，包括比利时和荷兰，最终日期定于 11 月 27 日在巴黎奥林匹亚举行。</p><p>根据歌手的声明，取消巡演的所有日期均可在购买时获得全额退款。这次巡演是为了支持这位法国歌手兼作曲家的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/christine-and-the-queens-paranoia-angels-true-love-review-3452224">《PARANOÏA, ANGELS, TRUE LOVE》</a> ，该专辑于今年 6 月发行，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/070-shake">070 Shake</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-dean">Mike Dean</a>等人。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cybum7oLEGP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06