2023/10/Steve-Harris-and-Janick-Gers-of-Iron-Maiden-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Steve-Harris-and-Janick-Gers-of-Iron-Maiden-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Steve-Harris-and-Janick-Gers-of-Iron-Maiden-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Steve-Harris-and-Janick-Gers-of-Iron-Maiden-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a>宣布了澳大利亚和新西兰的巡演日期，作为其更广泛的“Future Past”世界巡演的一部分。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-tobias-forge-interview-phantomine-genesis-jesus-knows-new-music-3427581">Ghost 乐队 Tobias Forge 谈论新翻唱 EP“Phantomime”：“它让我一睹我想去的地方”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支英国重金属乐队上周<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CyMftQetflK/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在社交媒体上分享的一段视频</a>中首次透露了这一日期。今天（10 月 16 日），正式演出已确定于明年 9 月举行，Iron Maiden 将于 9 月 1 日在珀斯的 RAC Arena 首次演出，另一场演出定于 9 月 4 日在阿德莱德娱乐中心举行。</p><p>此后，乐队将在墨尔本的 Rod Laver Arena（9 月 6 日）和布里斯班娱乐中心（9 月 10 日）演出，然后于 9 月 12 日敲定在悉尼 Qudos Bank Arena 的澳大利亚演出。Iron Maiden 还将在新西兰，9 月 16 日在奥克兰 Spark Arena。</p><p>金属核乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/killswitch-engage" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Killswitch Engage</a>将作为 Iron Maiden 澳大利亚和新西兰巡演所有日期的支持表演。 <a href="https://www.ironmaiden.com/fan-club" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Iron Maiden 粉丝俱乐部</a>的会员可以在 10 月 18 日星期三获得预售门票，并于 10 月 24 日<a href="https://www.ironmaiden.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星期二</a>通过 Iron Maiden 网站购买普通销售门票。</p><h2> <strong>Iron Maiden 2024 年澳大利亚和新西兰巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p> <strong>2024 年 9 月</strong><br /><strong>1 – 珀斯，西澳大利亚 @ RAC 竞技场</strong><br /><strong>4 – 阿德莱德，南澳大利亚@阿德莱德娱乐中心</strong><br /><strong>6 – 维多利亚州墨尔本@罗德·拉沃尔竞技场</strong><br /><strong>10 – 昆士兰州布里斯班@布里斯班娱乐中心</strong><br /><strong>12 – 新南威尔士州悉尼@Qudos Bank Arena</strong><br /> <strong>16 – 新西兰奥克兰 @ Spark Arena</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">惊喜，惊喜……The Future Past 巡演也将于 2024 年来到澳大利亚！</p><p> 2024 年 9 月：<br /> 01- RAC 竞技场，珀斯 – 澳大利亚<br />04 – 阿德莱德娱乐中心, 阿德莱德 – 澳大利亚<br />06 – 罗德拉沃尔竞技场，墨尔本 – 澳大利亚<br />10 – 布里斯班娱乐中心, 布里斯班 – 澳大利亚<br />12 – Qudos 银行… <a href="https://t.co/TXIN32p0jW">pic.twitter.com/TXIN32p0jW</a></p><p> - 铁娘子 (@IronMaiden) <a href="https://twitter.com/IronMaiden/status/1713646989462651238?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Iron Maiden 最后一次出现在澳大利亚是在 2020 年，作为他们的“野兽遗产”巡演的一部分。由于 COVID-19 大流行，该系列演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/iron-maiden-postpone-australian-tour-citing-coronavirus-performance-restrictions-2630931" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最终被推迟</a>。 “我们当时向所有人保证我们会回到澳大利亚，”铁娘子经理罗布·斯莫伍德在一份新闻声明中谈到即将到来的巡演时说道。 “我们始终信守承诺。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我们非常期待将这部令人惊叹的新节目带到南半球，并为我们忠实的澳大利亚粉丝提供最好的首秀节目。你可以放心，等待是值得的。”</p><p> Iron Maiden 的“Future Past”巡演是为了支持他们最新的 2021 年专辑“Senjutsu”。世界巡演于今年五月在斯洛文尼亚开始，随后乐队又前往英国、加拿大和美国。</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/iron-maiden-senjutsu-review-3035836">four-star review of &#39;Senjutsu&#39;</a> , <em>NME</em> described the album as “an instant classic,” saying the band&#39;s music is “more confident and idea-packed than ever before.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-2024-australia-new-zealand-tour-3515455">Iron Maiden announce 2024 tour dates for Australia and New Zealand</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 'Carrie' and 'Twin Peaks' actor Piper Laurie passes away, aged 91 https://www.nme.com/news/film/carrie-and-twin-peaks-actor-piper-laurie-passes-away-aged-91-3515449?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=carrie-and-twin-peaks-actor-piper-laurie-passes-away-aged-91Tom Disalvo Mon, 16 Oct 2023 04:34:21 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3515449 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Piper Laurie attends the TCM Classic Film Festival in 2022" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The Golden Age of Hollywood starlet had a film and television career spanning seven decades</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/carrie-and-twin-peaks-actor-piper-laurie-passes-away-aged-91-3515449">&#39;Carrie&#39; and &#39;Twin Peaks&#39; actor Piper Laurie passes away, aged 91</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Piper Laurie attends the TCM Classic Film Festival in 2022" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Piper-Laurie-attends-the-TCM-Classic-Film-Festival-in-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Three-time Academy Award nominee Piper Laurie has passed away at the age of 91.</p><p> The actor, known for her scene-stealing roles in <i>Carrie</i> and <i>Twin Peaks,</i> died of old age on Saturday, October 14, her manager Marion Rosenberg confirmed in a statement to <i><a href="https://apnews.com/article/piper-laurie-dies-carrie-twin-peaks-bd5ad2a7524dd50a3c356558728d358f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Associated Press</a> .</i></p><p> “[Laurie] was a superb talent and a wonderful human being,” Rosenberg said. Born in 1932, Laurie&#39;s career in Hollywood spanned seven decades, and included acclaimed performances in films like 1961 drama <i>The Hustler</i> opposite Paul Newman, the film adaptation of Stephen King&#39;s <i>Carrie</i> and the 1986 romance, <i>Children of a Lesser God.</i></p><p> Alongside those notable film roles – which each earned her an Oscar nomination – Laurie graced the silver screen with television appearances on <i>Matlock</i> , <i>Murder, She Wrote</i> , <i>Frasier</i> and <i>Twin Peaks,</i> the last of which earned her two Emmy nominations in the 1990s.</p><p> Long considered one of the faces of Hollywood&#39;s Golden Age, Laurie attracted headlines for her brief romance with Ronald Reagan, whom she starred opposite in the 1950 comedy <i>Louisa.</i></p><p> Alongside Reagan, Laurie was known for her film credits with fellow actors and Golden Age stars Rock Hudson, Tony Curtis and Rory Calhoun, whom she appeared alongside in titles like <i>The Golden Blade</i> , <i>Johnny Dark</i> and <i>Ain&#39;t Misbehavin&#39;</i> , respectively. Despite her success, Laurie stepped away from acting for many years, in search of “an existence more meaningful for me”, she explained in a 1990 interview.</p><p> During her time away from the limelight, Laurie moved to a farmhouse in Woodstock, New York, and married film critic Joseph Morgenstern. The pair adopted their child, daughter Ann Grace, in 1971. Laurie&#39;s career was reignited following her role as Margaret White in <i>Carrie,</i> portraying the deranged, fanatically religious mother of the titular high schooler to universal acclaim.</p><p> <i>Carrie</i> went on to become a box office success, sparking a craze for teenage horror films and earning Laurie her second Oscar nomination. With renewed interest in her Hollywood career, Laurie appeared in a slew of television shows including <i>Law &amp; Order</i> and <i>Will</i> <em>&amp;</em> <em>Grace</em> .</p><p> The actor&#39;s most recent film credit was for the 2018 crime drama <i>White Boy Rick,</i> starring Matthew McConaughey.<i>  </i></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/carrie-and-twin-peaks-actor-piper-laurie-passes-away-aged-91-3515449">&#39;Carrie&#39; and &#39;Twin Peaks&#39; actor Piper Laurie passes away, aged 91</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
